  "response": "If you've lost your prescription slip for Norco, here are some steps you can take:\n\n1. Contact your prescribing healthcare provider directly. They can:\n- Reissue the prescription\n- Send a new prescription to your pharmacy electronically\n- Provide a new written prescription\n\n2. Check if your pharmacy or doctor has a copy of the original prescription on file.\n\n3. Important notes:\n- For controlled substances like Norco, there are strict regulations\n- You cannot simply call the pharmacy and request a refill\n- You must get a new prescription directly from your healthcare provider\n- Your doctor may require an in-person appointment\n\n4. Do not attempt to forge or alter a prescription, as this is illegal and can result in serious legal consequences.\n\nAlways work directly with your healthcare provider to resolve prescription issues.",
